Title: Śahazāda Dārāśikoha
Subtitle: dahaśata kā daṃśa
Author: Śatrughna Prasāda
Summary: Based on the life of Dārā Shikūh, Prince, son of Shahjahan, Emperor of India, 1615-1659.

Title: Saṅkshiptanāṭyaśāstram
Author: Bharata Muni
Summary: Abridged version of Nāṭyaśāstra, a treatise on ancient Indian dramaturgy, histrionics, and dance.

Title: Shreshtha Vyangya Kathayen
Author: Kanhaiya Lal Nandan
Summary: Selected humorous and satirical stories by various Hindi authors.
